# Python Runtime

- For Python commands in this repository, use `${workspaceFolder}/.venv/bin/python`.
- Do not use system Python, Homebrew Python, or bare `python`/`python3` unless the user explicitly requests it.
- Treat `.venv/` as out of scope for reading or editing, but it is allowed to execute `.venv/bin/python` and installed console scripts.
- If dependency resolution fails, report that the virtualenv needs updating instead of switching interpreters.
